---
import BookButton from './BookButton.astro';
---

<section id="story" class="section-padding section-alt scroll-mt-20">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <h2 class="text-heading">Why I do this</h2>
    <div class="mt-5 space-y-4 text-text-muted">
      <p>
        During a recent recruiting cycle, I submitted more than 300 applications and faced the same bottlenecks many students experience—unclear positioning, inconsistent applications, and difficulty explaining my work quickly.
      </p>
      <p>
        I refined how I presented my projects, built a more focused search, and eventually received four technical-internship offers, including final rounds with companies like Amazon and Oracle. I am now a Software Engineering Intern at Splunk while finishing my CS degree at UIUC.
      </p>
      <p>
        I built this coaching program to help other students present their work honestly and organize a search that fits their goals—without inflated promises.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <BookButton />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
